@startuml sequence_meeting_rsvp
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Meeting RSVP Flow [L2-029]

actor "Team Member" as User
participant "Meetings Page\n/teams/meetings" as MeetUI
participant "API Client\nlib/api/scheduling.ts" as Client
participant "Meeting Routes\n/api/scheduling/meetings" as API
database "PostgreSQL\nscheduling schema" as DB

User -> MeetUI: Navigate to /teams/meetings
MeetUI -> Client: getMeetings()
Client -> API: GET /api/scheduling/meetings
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM meetings\nJOIN meeting_attendees
DB --> API: meetings with attendees
API --> Client: 200 JSON
Client --> MeetUI: Render date-grouped\nmeeting list

User -> MeetUI: View meeting details
MeetUI -> Client: getMeeting(meetingId)
Client -> API: GET /api/scheduling/meetings/[id]
API -> DB: SELECT meeting + attendees\nWHERE id = ?
DB --> API: meeting detail
API --> Client: 200 JSON
Client --> MeetUI: Show title, time, location,\nattendees, RSVP status

User -> MeetUI: Click "Accept" (or "Decline")
MeetUI -> Client: updateMeeting(meetingId, {\n  rsvpStatus: "accepted" })
Client -> API: PUT /api/scheduling/meetings/[id]
API -> DB: UPDATE meeting_attendees\nSET rsvp_status = 'accepted'\nWHERE employee_id = ?
DB --> API: updated
API --> Client: 200 OK
Client --> MeetUI: Refresh RSVP badge

@enduml
